🧩 Scramble Game

A simple and fun word scramble game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The player is presented with a scrambled word and must guess the correct word within a limited number of attempts.

🚀 Features

- Random word scrambling
- User-friendly interface
- Score tracking or limited guesses (optional)
- Responsive design
- Instant feedback on user input

 🎮 How to Play

1. A scrambled word will appear on the screen.
2. You must guess the original word.
3. Type your answer and click ||ubmit||.
4. The game will check your answer and respond accordingly.
5. Try to guess as many correct words as possible!

 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript


